$07         *help line (display length is shorter than field length)
$01         *help line attribute for visible port
$09         *help line attribute for additional cursor
$07         *tabulator line
$70         *line numbers
$07         *debugger line
$70         *warnings
$F0         *error messages
$01         *editing line if not active
